advocate for funding
for mental health

00:29:21.550 --> 00:29:24.700
or getting more mental
health providers.

00:29:24.700 --> 00:29:27.370
If you care about
climate change,

00:29:27.370 --> 00:29:31.620
an existential threat to us
all, get involved in that.

