And you'll be
surprised, you become

00:29:33.820 --> 00:29:35.890
a foot soldier in
an organization,

00:29:35.890 --> 00:29:38.230
how quickly you
become an officer

00:29:38.230 --> 00:29:40.330
and how quickly you're
lobbying Congress.

00:29:40.330 --> 00:29:41.630
And it makes a difference.

00:29:41.630 --> 00:29:42.745
It really does.

00:29:42.745 --> 00:29:43.764
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:29:43.764 --> 00:29:44.680
AL FRANKEN: Thank you.

00:29:44.680 --> 00:29:46.634
JAIME GREEN: You said
earlier that your sort

00:29:46.634 --> 00:29:48.925
of overarching goal is to
serve the people of Minnesota

00:29:48.925 --> 00:29:51.250
when you're in the Senate.

00:29:51.250 --> 00:29:55.300
How much do phone calls or
emails from your constituents

00:29:55.300 --> 00:29:56.560
