I'm Joy.

00:30:16.940 --> 00:30:19.715
I actually graduated last
year from Carleton College.

00:30:19.715 --> 00:30:21.100
AL FRANKEN: Oh, great school.

00:30:21.100 --> 00:30:22.040
AUDIENCE: And
speaking of getting

00:30:22.040 --> 00:30:23.965
involved, I've actually
been to your office

00:30:23.965 --> 00:30:26.785
