00:30:50.130 --> 00:30:51.620
for where we are right now.

00:30:51.620 --> 00:30:55.040
I'm curious if you could speak
to any coordinated efforts

00:30:55.040 --> 00:30:58.506
on behalf of the party to
really go back on the offense

00:30:58.506 --> 00:31:00.380
and take back some power,
rather than waiting

00:31:00.380 --> 00:31:03.274
until the elections in 2018.

00:31:03.274 --> 00:31:04.690
AL FRANKEN: Well,
we have a system

00:31:04.690 --> 00:31:08.590
