We have districts
in America that

00:42:43.640 --> 00:42:50.240
are very blue, like in
New York, or very red.

00:42:50.240 --> 00:42:52.820
If you look at a
map of the country,

00:42:52.820 --> 00:42:54.090
you know where those are.

00:42:54.090 --> 00:43:04.740
So I think you guys could
Google those pretty well, right?

00:43:04.740 --> 00:43:07.400
So some of you, I
think, are paid OK.

00:43:07.400 --> 00:43:13.952
And you can actually
give money to candidates

00:43:13.952 --> 00:43:15.410
who are running in
swing districts,

00:43:15.410 --> 00:43:19.040
for example, or to organizations
that believe in the things

00:43:19.040 --> 00:43:19.700
you believe in.

