can join advocacy
groups that speak

00:43:28.040 --> 00:43:31.890
to everybody if it's about
an issue that you care about.

00:43:31.890 --> 00:43:35.360
If you care about housing, if
you care about clean water,

00:43:35.360 --> 00:43:37.280
you can join
advocacy groups that

00:43:37.280 --> 00:43:39.200
are national advocacy groups.

00:43:39.200 --> 00:43:46.810
And then you're talking about
an issue that lobbies everybody

00:43:46.810 --> 00:43:49.220
in Congress or tries
to speak to everybody--

00:43:49.220 --> 00:43:52.530
and not only that, but
people in state houses

00:43:52.530 --> 00:43:55.280
and in local government.

00:43:55.280 --> 00:43:57.080
And all of that is
very, very important.

