00:46:38.370 --> 00:46:45.840
try to talk about how it
really is, how it really works.

00:46:45.840 --> 00:46:47.750
And not in a cynical way.

00:46:47.750 --> 00:46:49.550
JAIME GREEN: No.

00:46:49.550 --> 00:46:50.762
[LAUGHTER]

00:46:50.762 --> 00:46:52.470
AL FRANKEN: This is
how we're going to do

00:46:52.470 --> 00:46:54.730
