example and showing us

00:50:01.400 --> 00:50:05.330
that you can go from
commenting on the process

00:50:05.330 --> 00:50:07.280
to actually do something
and living that.

00:50:07.280 --> 00:50:08.090
So thank you.

00:50:08.090 --> 00:50:09.673
AL FRANKEN: Thank
you for saying that.

